task.description:
This corrects visibilities, and/or their (u, v, w) positions, for various effects that can be calculated without fitting a model to the data.
The effects include: \begin{itemize} \item calculating (u, v, w) coordinates,
\item changing the refcode (i.e. B1950 to J2000 or 2006.78), \item changing the projection, as in (-)NCP to SIN, \item refocusing (Not yet incorporated). \end{itemize}
